      Every AIM RNS is assessed against a structured signal framework designed specifically for the structural realities of the AIM market.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Categorised by signal type</li>
      <li>Impact scored (1–5) with consistent criteria</li>
      <li>Structured, decision-ready summary</li>
      <li>Key context surfaced (dilution, guidance, cash, terms)</li>
      <li>Prioritised by materiality — not just chronology</li>
    </ul>

